      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont even know why i'm typing this. it just feels like there's nothing left. 10 years. just gone. i wake up and for a split second i think she's still there and then it hits me all over again and it's like... i can't do this anymore. i literally cannot imagine waking up to another morning like this. it's just too much.",
